  Sharing two pictures of the trio looking all grown up with his 54,000 Instagram followers, Tyger wrote: “Family. #grateful.” Ramona, who portrayed the family's cheeky youngster Karen, added the snaps to her Instagram, while Ben Brockman star Daniel re-shared one of the pics to his story with the caption: “Suspiciously nice photo.” Outnumbered ran for five series on the BBC between 2007 and 2014. Tyger, Daniel and Ramona played the children of long-suffering couple Pete (Hugh Dennis) and Sue (Claire Skinner).   